headline: Crypto Has an Ally in the White House. What’s Ahead for Digital Currencies in 2025.
summary: Crypto die-hards are anticipating a golden age for digital assets under President-elect  Donald Trump.  The price of bitcoin breached $100,000 for the first time in December and has more than doubled in 2024.  The president-elect has promised to make the U.S. the “crypto capital of the planet.”
